  "2026-07-07T07:30:43.098Z",claude-code-agent,"Implementation start: bundling GH-476 context --max-items alias with GH-474 hybrid search --limit because both reduce agent token/context round-trips. Duplicate checks found pm-gdi7 as the broader unknown-option engine follow-up, but this item has specific GH-476 acceptance criteria."
  "2026-07-07T08:04:32.571Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: implemented hidden pm context --max-items alias as an exact --limit synonym across runtime parsing, option normalization, context flag contracts, and generated contract snapshots. Verification passed: linked focused pm test (288 tests), pnpm build, node scripts/run-tests.mjs test (264 files / 5449 tests), node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (100% statements/branches/functions/lines), pnpm typecheck, pnpm lint, pnpm security:scan, pnpm contracts:check. Packed-install dogfood in /tmp/tmp.FlmKN3LY44 confirmed npx pm context --json --max-items 1 returns filters.limit=1 and one low_level row. GitHub refresh found no open Dependabot security alerts; open Dependabot PRs #462/#465 remain separate dependency-update PRs and are behind base."
